{
  "blocks": [
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_7656efb2cd8bf2d81abcef52",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "一位舞者的故事：菲莉丝·斯皮拉的故事",
        "text_hash": "5aedc964bc432b73c5ef6383820cd5167c9a290c604a365a8ef64905ca6f9e77",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_291be919e5502017e0e02dca",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "菲莉丝的妈妈和爸爸抱着他们可爱的女宝宝。每个人都面带笑容，十分开心。",
        "text_hash": "f3e2ac489cd9397eff272487cb2ae3984afa2ebcbc6cfb1209c3708e43dd5e80",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d06af557ad044465dbddee82",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "从前，就在不远的地方，一个名叫菲莉丝的宝宝为芭蕾而生。",
        "text_hash": "cb0f52d213226f46aae7df9dccad80a3401eb9296f56ade12c87e7211df09164",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_65267e7901b9b7400430985c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "相爱的两个人，她的妈妈和爸爸，那时还不知道他们拥有怎样一位舞者。",
        "text_hash": "02aaaddeaa9004196f71c6a5bebf86f0b5ffe24e2eec203c5241649a6b55064a",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_00665781ed1a265a7e0965c6",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "小菲莉丝和另外两个小女孩一起为她们严格的芭蕾老师跳舞。",
        "text_hash": "37358bbe6d94670924270accf23ee44629ac42f0b5ac14cba64014a5847f5079",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3b311819bb10038f6154fdea",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "菲莉丝四岁时就让我们看得入迷：她用小鸭子般的脚尖轻弹动作打动了老师们。",
        "text_hash": "caaf5f40dc43b4b7c4eeadffc94a224f8b17e7314c240d53520ba899183358d9",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_6a63ec05ae99737582b2d7d5",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "上学前和放学后，她每天都跳舞。没有什么比芭蕾更让菲莉丝开心。",
        "text_hash": "4cd3f36e088997a8b598a8b9721b37b4e9bb02245bf97f47af4f11be2837c97f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_c07f2dfe946a7660482c508e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "十几岁的菲莉丝穿着漂亮的黄色连衣裙，在伦敦的一块街牌旁旋转。背景中可以看到大本钟。",
        "text_hash": "f1dafe0a3f9a23f4d9cd84aa16ca1f9b3a56d94a87a6fd13364a4a94d1b1aae0",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_baf73d12c1135142e05dcf21",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "世界很快就会看到，年仅十五岁的她前往伦敦，去实现自己的梦想。",
        "text_hash": "878f05cae83269f5a27c0a1c7c8509111e2790f64ce825a4ee15a833edab2f02",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_259d552374c94ff30313cc3a",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "远离家乡和朋友，她开始了全新的生活。皇家芭蕾舞学校很快就会对她刮目相看！",
        "text_hash": "e1be451f170942fc919a2228aed2f4adb00f5027e13d41e7172b7296155d360b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_92c172c816ae7d9d5bbac6eb",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "菲莉丝与一位英俊的男舞者一起踮脚跳舞。",
        "text_hash": "3b3710d71a9d7e24116e5e04996b74ac3d0400b01c9d6d4d8b2f5fe7509ca561",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_30b94ffd0f13919560af7912",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "她跳《天鹅湖》时，那表演配得上女王观看！经过多年旋转练习，她终于到了被世人看见的时候！",
        "text_hash": "fd82448ca0dcaa558c3cae8bad3f3a6f914b7973a0c97773ac0781c83b7360fb",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a67e6dbc7c71f3e1c108e1d9",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "她登上舞台，跳跃、旋转，四处舞动，所有人都面带笑容！他们鼓掌，也大声欢呼！",
        "text_hash": "625f6032f252a597a438bedc0f7e242513cbb5d80c63fdbeb1bfd7e46996c509",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_fe0b0c53fa6c795a679d1c50",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "菲莉丝提着一个手提箱，跃过地球。她穿着一条饰有世界各国旗帜流苏的连衣裙。",
        "text_hash": "c28b1fa62c700080cb27b8d08d50076093771799a16dc9b8af5a391f8055747a",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_cfcc760fa61259a2b8a45255",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "从墨西哥到加拿大，从美国到法国，人人都邀请她前去访问和跳舞。",
        "text_hash": "83f8ed2af6ae3ac4f62102456744f6d773d5a68ca34be13405b7b3d6e1f389f9",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_5dce025b3b8afebaf376e082",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "她与皇家芭蕾舞团以及所有朋友一起，把对舞蹈的热爱传播开来，让它永不止息。",
        "text_hash": "f34b59af254c5005dfc61abc2631961e5723116648d0e28d0ef89eb73fad6d96",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_398ad020a037c5537f58c2be",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "菲莉丝怀里抱着一面南非国旗。她穿着一条受非洲风格启发的连衣裙，背景中可以看到桌山。",
        "text_hash": "66e58d1706c67b9ae9086843ef178eaf0db9294680eee48cda11c04a7367fb92",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_e76468104fc781c059d5ec78",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "然而，菲莉丝想念家乡，她与家乡分别太久了。她渴望回去，重新开始。",
        "text_hash": "ce60276f1ceb64fed798ba93aa2e36a60ca89acc9d2d91eb13b1c43d66d55d6d",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_23215ebe40405309b862c232",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "于是她跳跃着、奔跃着回到她美丽的土地，再一次走在南非的沙地上。",
        "text_hash": "f5e78eb6839199d9f51f3e5edf1f9ad0e98cdf16a07da0bccbca6dd2d317461d",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_cbd552d8d8b9a3b9dd6164ce",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "菲莉丝在以时钟为背景的舞台上跳舞。",
        "text_hash": "edc6a27846bb743866f5631708a74899f2da83febee0c38e0884e3c900a307ff",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_45f06527fca96f0839655cfc",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "菲莉丝深知，舞蹈不只是乐趣：她日夜努力，并在辛勤付出中成长。",
        "text_hash": "9d2c0c96dd85c750be751844450e0b78c3130b540b81cc8d36d86a12c6b67f12",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a9440d33eff7f206a83128c4",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "她总是微笑着、不知疲倦，无论顺境还是艰难时刻，她都追求做到最好。“好”从来不够。",
        "text_hash": "b8ebf6faa00b00c248e9146975d0944062c4bf3f78bb637c0bda0078557c2481",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_151f2581e7c70819066eca5e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "菲莉丝穿着漂亮的蓝色演出服，与一位强壮的男舞者在舞台上共舞。观众赞赏地鼓掌。",
        "text_hash": "c10d0bb8280c136cd89804a7f9367c2273304d77c447b23c64561d7829253f4a",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_2432a18526fc7fe8f2009d66",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "《罗密欧与朱丽叶》、《天鹅湖》和《吉赛尔》。她让每一位观众都沉醉在她的魅力之中。",
        "text_hash": "885879c76453e40093b06e2fd086a9f8b9b58474562182b29be662b82f4b33c3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ac57721732177379fc9ee2c9",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "有加里·伯恩在她身旁，爱德华·格雷林也在，她的舞蹈在每一篇评论中都如魔法般动人。",
        "text_hash": "44a5eee64c4719c747b7de14ed0f4f9495df9299f804955d4cb9c4886ae22161",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_e1250bb0d123f29d78415ec2",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "玫瑰铺在菲莉丝脚边，一条绶带宣布着她的新头衔，她满怀感激地握紧双手。",
        "text_hash": "a66a241813fe2110345ab42548ea35ecf28e4b421c3db1ee7c4f297fb5b855fc",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d0a270cdcab3408be74dd9b9",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "当你经受考验时，回报终会到来。有一天，南非会称她为最优秀的舞者：",
        "text_hash": "611159b969fb8a7513b7d855270b307105b9ae0f11984d9ee48721c05bf755f1",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_82de4c1bf9b1ebf32db102db",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“绝对首席芭蕾舞女演员”，最伟大的舞者，这是她永远的头衔。",
        "text_hash": "826d9dc7c6ab8ef0e7cf214727315656c0181e570f069b9af784525c5dcc4628",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ee1f5ba97f40f7bd31adf10a",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "菲莉丝别无所求。",
        "text_hash": "d924b42dff438bd14edfba8f1c8fe3506fff152eab981ec9a39879360947ecb9",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_b21bd07c7eb8dad649036bc0",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "菲莉丝深情地凝望着新婚丈夫的眼睛，他将她一把揽入怀中，跳起他们的婚礼之舞。",
        "text_hash": "b01ce9e2426f619ab1d4ba1f9c276306c97554408988a8de27f4168c5d404743",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3cfefa9b9f587915d9346253",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "不久，菲莉丝遇见了菲利普·博伊德，也找到了爱情，他本人也是一名舞者！他们俩都欣喜若狂。",
        "text_hash": "c9c87325f3b7cdf5594760fed515ff89a2107df06f89b25d6d61784c7ecf97e1",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_52634508ea504bb96404a3bb",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "相爱的他们很快结婚了，并一起跳舞。若有机会，再没有比这更好的伴侣了！",
        "text_hash": "4f0548969b47c2c4c4f302963df1f0b9e2bee9a842b51d4851f7e77e441f1f2e",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_9245048fe39ed13b188b1e8d",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "菲莉丝在舞蹈课上纠正一个小女孩的手臂姿势。另外两个孩子正在练习舞步。",
        "text_hash": "67149b2f2c23ac9cb5c8b575a824b60e2a01a3ea30220e206a33a27da82682c8",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_8270b273d1bda4b475d9985e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "他们没有孩子，却从不难过，因为他们有办法帮助所有的妈妈和爸爸。",
        "text_hash": "5055184ced342590d9b7bbe0b5951c6c8e4aeceb8c03d84c2e17e1d4637b0a8c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_fc635123b784de801f0e65fa",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "他们的学校 Dance For All 会给孩子们一个机会，让来自各行各业的孩子学习并热爱舞蹈。",
        "text_hash": "d61c421be5f5073687351e745236d129a25ad760bb445aa18e23fc21be9e1a46",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_03b419b4fb0ecdd8fd58ebf0",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "菲莉丝望向读者，另外五位芭蕾舞者在她周围的页面上起舞。",
        "text_hash": "71e6db86636047af4e2811522f82a921f4d34cca8ff08955e636575a7ee04dc4",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_767c7e78806634997514ea82",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "她献给世界的天赋和她所有的成功，帮助别人意识到他们也能做到最好。",
        "text_hash": "8d65c048c29a2db13caea6cd713ee5436b1643ce07cffe77886ddde47e4e252c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_9b37c12e3701716ebb98b015"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3b23eb748608ba3bf09713bd",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
